title: Ruthie's Bagel Dish
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers in-house-made vegan cream cheese, gluten-free bagels and waffles, vegan ice cream, and soy milk for coffee. Clearly listed vegetarian menu includes a rueben, soy hot dogs, tofu quesadilla, vegetarian chili, vegetarian soup of the day, of which some are vegan or can be made vegan. Serves breakfast and lunch only.
